  <brief_title>Efficacy of TAK-438 Compared to Placebo in the Treatment of Non-Erosive Gastroesophageal Reflux Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Randomized, Double Blind, Placebo Control, Multicenter Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of TAK- 438 (10 and 20 mg Once-Daily) in Patients With Non-Erosive Gastroesophageal Reflux Disease.</official_title>
